&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-maven-wrapper-for-consistent-version"&gt;Use Maven Wrapper for Consistent Version&lt;/h3&gt;
